:00'),(246,6,30,'daily_monthly','Ensure the radio status is healthy','Radio Tower/Radio Modems','Monthly','POWER and STATUS LEDs shall not show red indication','','',NULL,'2025-12-15 23:57:00'),(247,7,30,'daily_monthly','Visually examine all the communication cables are connected properly and radio modems had tighten the corresponding screws','Radio Tower/Radio Modems','Monthly','Ensure the tightness of the cables and modem modules','','',NULL,'2025-12-15 23:57:00'),(248,8,30,'daily_monthly','Ensure the reverse power of Transmitter and receiver antennas is less than 1W','Radio Tower / Radio Modems','Monthly','Measure reverse power of all 4 coaxial cables and record. Ensure reverse power is less than 1W for all cables','','',NULL,'2025-12-15 23:57:00'),(249,9,30,'daily_monthly','Check the 110V DC output for Aviation Warning Lamp in the Location Box is correct and lamp is glowing','Radio Tower / Radio Modems','Monthly','Check for correctness','','',NULL,'2025-12-15 23:57:00'),(250,10,30,'daily_monthly','Clean surface of the Earth electrode /MEEB/SEEB','Earthing,LA &amp;SPD','Monthly','Surface should be kept clean','','',NULL,'2025-12-15 23:57:00'),(251,11,30,'daily_monthly','Measure the Resistance of the Ring Earth If possible, fill water in the Earth Pits to keep low soil resistance','Earthing,LA &amp;SPD','Monthly','Resistance Should be 1Ώ(Ohm)','','',NULL,'2025-12-15 23:57:00'),(252,12,30,'daily_monthly','Check the SPD devices for any signs of physical degradation','Earthing,LA &amp;SPD','Monthly','Check the Indication LED status of SPD. (If SPD indicates FAIL then replace)','','',NULL,'2025-12-15 23:57:00'),(253,13,30,'daily_monthly','Check Lightning Arrestor at the top of the tower connection at copper wire to Ring earth. Tighten all the connections/Terminations','Earthing,LA &amp;SPD','Monthly','All the connections to be tightened.','','',NULL,'2025-12-15 23:57:00'),(254,14,30,'daily_monthly','Check the serviceability SPD at IPS 110 V DC-DC converter','Earthing,LA &amp;SPD','Monthly','Check the Indication LED status of SPD. (If SPD indicates FAIL then replace)','','',NULL,'2025-12-15 23:57:00'),(255,15,30,'daily_monthly','Check the serviceability SPD at Radio MODEM','Earthing,LA &amp;SPD','Monthly','Check the Indication LED status of SPD. (If SPD indicates FAIL then replace)','','',NULL,'2025-12-15 23:57:00'),(256,16,30,'daily_monthly','Ensure buttons are working properly','SOIP in SM ROOM','Monthly','Insert SM key and turn to keyIN position. Press and hold each button for 6 seconds and wait for button stuck fault. After releasing, button stuck fault shall disappear from LCD.','','',NULL,'2025-12-15 23:57:00'),(257,17,30,'daily_monthly','Ensure SM Key is working properly','SOIP in SM ROOM','Monthly','The above operation shall fail when SM key is OUT.','','',NULL,'2025-12-15 23:57:00');
