) Supply','21.6V to 28.8V DCto be observed','','',NULL,97,'2025-11-27 23:48:18','2025-11-28 04:18:18'),(21,10,'power','Check the voltages at Equipment end of EXTERNAL','21.6V to 28.8V DCto be observed','','',NULL,97,'2025-11-27 23:48:19','2025-11-28 04:18:19'),(22,11,'power','Check the all wago fuse indications','Disconnect type fuse wago indications should not glow','','',NULL,97,'2025-11-27 23:48:19','2025-11-28 04:18:19');
